'''''Ayomoy''''' (''The man who would not die'') was a popular [[Bangladesh]]i television serial, written by [[Humayun Ahmed]] and directed by [[Nawazish Ali Khan]], originally aired on [[Bangladesh Television|Bangladesh television]] in 1991-92. Blending fact with fiction it is set in the period of [[British raj]], the story centres on a declining Bengali [[zamindar]] (landlord) family.

