[[File:32th SANOG International conference closing program in Dhaka, 2018 (3).jpg|thumb|300px|32nd SANOG International conference closing program in Dhaka, 2018]]
The '''South Asian Network Operators' Group''' ('''SANOG''') is a South Asian counterpart to [[North American Network Operators' Group|NANOG]]. Like NANOG, SANOG operates a [[mailing list]] for operators of Asian data networks, including [[Internet service provider|ISPs]].

