{{Infobox Union |name= UNTC-CS |country= [[Cape Verde]] |affiliation= [[International Trade Union Confederation|ITUC]] |members= 15,000 |full_name= União Nacional dos Trabalhadores de Cabo Verde – Central Sindical |native_name= |image= |founded= 1978 |current= |head= |dissolved_date= |dissolved_state= |merged_into= |office= [[Praia]], Cape Verde |people= [[Júlio Ascensão Silva]] |website={{url|https://untc-cs.cv}} |footnotes= }} <!-- Include all unused fields for future use. See [[template talk:Infobox Union]] for usage. -->
The '''UNTC-CS''' ({{lang|pt|União Nacional dos Trabalhadores de Cabo Verde – Central Sindical}}, English translation: "National Union of Workers of Cape Verde - Central Union") is a [[national trade union centre]] in [[Cape Verde]]. It was founded in 1978, and is a member of the [[International Trade Union Confederation]] <ref>[https://untc-cs.cv/about/ História], UNTC-CS</ref> It has about 15,000 members (2018).<ref>[https://www.ituc-csi.org/IMG/pdf/18_07_10_list_of_affiliates_ac.pdf List of affiliated organisations], ITUC</ref>
